# Cortex Monolith Overview

This repository is the **modular monolith** (not microservices). Work from the repo root.

## Read first

1. `docs/engineering/README.md`
2. `docs/engineering/how-we-work/feature-placement.md`
3. `docs/engineering/architecture/module-boundaries.md`
4. `AGENTS.md`

Comparison with reference project 2: `docs/engineering/reference/comparison-project-2.md`

## Repo map

```
apps/cortex-server/     Ôćĺ thin FastAPI shell (routers, app.state)
apps/sync-worker/       Ôćĺ Celery -Q sync
apps/ingestion-worker/  Ôćĺ Celery -Q ingestion
apps/web-client/        Ôćĺ React (Vite)
scripts/                Ôćĺ dev.sh, seed-neo4j.sh

packages/module-platform/    Ôćĺ auth, cases, audit, system
packages/module-documents/   Ôćĺ Document CRUD + lifecycle (ONLY status owner)
packages/module-chat/        Ôćĺ Redis threads, chat API
packages/module-sync/        Ôćĺ SyncOrchestrator, job trigger/polling
packages/module-dms-sync/    Ôćĺ DMS delta sync (Celery)
packages/module-ingestion/   Ôćĺ OCR Ôćĺ chunk Ôćĺ embed Ôćĺ Weaviate (Celery)
packages/module-ai/          Ôćĺ LangGraph agents (rag, legal, nlp)

libs/cortex-core/            Ôćĺ ports, enums, settings, Celery, SearchPort
